  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK676">
<l>muṭivu miṭaiyūṟu muṟṟiyāṅ keytum </l>
<l>paṭupayaṉum pārttuc ceyal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>An act is to be performed after considering the exertion required, the obstacles to be encountered, and the great profit to be gained (on its completion)</l>
            </lg>
